{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/swiftui_RestAPI/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"swiftui-restapi-get으로-json-데이터-받기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#swiftui-restapi-get%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-json-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%EB%B0%9B%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"swiftui restapi get으로 json 데이터 받기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SwiftUI RestAPI GET으로 json 데이터 받기</h3>\n<p>SwiftUI에서 RestAPI를 통해 json 데이터를 받아서 처리해야할 때 사용한 코드이다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"restapi-get통신\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#restapi-get%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0\" aria-label=\"restapi get통신 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>RestAPI GET통신</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">SwiftUI</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProgramCardViewModel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">ObservableObject</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">fetchPrograms</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> url <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"http://localhost:8080/user/all\"</span>\n    \n    @<span class=\"token builtin\">Published</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Programs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token builtin\">Program</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function\">fetchPrograms</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">guard</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> url <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> url<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token builtin\">URLSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shared<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">dataTask</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>with<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> url<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> resp<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> err<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span>\n            <span class=\"token builtin\">DispatchQueue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>main<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>async <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">Programs</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">try</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span> <span class=\"token function\">JSONDecoder</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">decode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token builtin\">Program</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">self</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> from<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> data<span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resume</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function\">getPrograms</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token builtin\">Program</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">Programs</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>url에 주소를 저장한 후 URLSession을 통해 데이터를 불러와 JSONDecoder를 이용해 json 형태로 만들었다.</p>\n<p>해당 클래스가 생성될 때 서버에서 데이터를 불러와야 했기 때문에 init에서 함수를 호출해 주었다.</p>\n<p>불러온 데이터는 Program배열에 저장 되는데 해당 변수를 @Published로 선언해야 변화를 감지할 수 있다.</p>\n<br>\n<br>\n뷰에선 해당 클래스를 선언해준 후 getPrograms 을 통해 배열을 받아와 ForEach로 뿌려주면 된다.","excerpt":"SwiftUI RestAPI GET으로 json 데이터 받기 SwiftUI에서 RestAPI를 통해 json 데이터를 받아서 처리해야할 때 사용한 코드이다. RestAPI GET통신 url에 주소를 저장한 후 URLSession을 통해 데이터를 불러…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/swiftui_RestAPI/#swiftui-restapi-get%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-json-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-%EB%B0%9B%EA%B8%B0\">SwiftUI RestAPI GET으로 json 데이터 받기</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/swiftui_RestAPI/#restapi-get%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0\">RestAPI GET통신</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/swiftui_RestAPI/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"SwiftUI RestAPI GET으로 json 데이터 받기","date":"Apr 14, 2021","tags":["SwiftUI"],"keywords":["MojitoBar","Ju dongseok"],"update":"Apr 14, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/swiftui_RestAPI/","series":[],"lastmod":"2021-04-14"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2027115977","694178885"]}